<tr>
<td class="list-key">视觉特效</td>
<td class="list-value">Björn Mayer、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E8%89%BE%E9%87%8C%E5%85%8B%C2%B7%E5%B7%B4%E5%B7%B4">艾里克·巴巴</a>、David Burton、Simon Carr、<a target=_blank href="/item/Thilo%20Ewers">Thilo Ewers</a></td>
</tr>
