<a name="角色介绍" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="para-title level-2" label-module="para-title">
<h2 class="title-text"><span class="title-prefix">遗落战境</span>角色介绍</h2>
<a class="edit-icon j-edit-link" data-edit-dl="3" href="javascript:;"><em class="cmn-icon wiki-lemma-icons wiki-lemma-icons_edit-lemma"></em>编辑</a>
</div>
<div class="anchor-list">
<a name="juesejieshao" class="lemma-anchor " ></a>
</div><div class="lemmaWgt-roleIntroduction">
<ul>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E9%81%97%E8%90%BD%E6%88%98%E5%A2%83/4967316/0/cefc1e178a82b901c18699e37a8da9773912ef33?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/-Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D284%2C0%2C316%2C451%3Bw%3D552%3Bq%3D70/sign=372733803da85edfeec3a46374663117/cefc1e178a82b901c18699e37a8da9773912ef33.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
杰克·哈勃<div></div>
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
汤姆·克鲁斯
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
孟令军;桂楠
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
杰克·哈勃是幸存者之一，与维卡共同留守地球，是遗落地球上最后的侦察机维修员，专门负责扫描受损的无人巡逻机。直到有一天他发现了一个遗弃的太空舱。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E9%81%97%E8%90%BD%E6%88%98%E5%A2%83/4967316/0/2fdda3cc7cd98d10004e49e1283fb80e7aec9043?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D196%2C0%2C360%2C513%3Bw%3D552%3Bq%3D70/sign=86a6d16b8ed6277ffd5d687815092606/2fdda3cc7cd98d10004e49e1283fb80e7aec9043.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
马尔科姆·比奇
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
摩根·弗里曼
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E9%99%86%E5%BB%BA%E8%89%BA">陆建艺</a>;程玉珠
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div>马尔科姆·比奇是一位神秘首领，肩负指引杰克·哈伯的重任。引领杰克发现他自己身世的秘密，以及地球毁灭的真相。经过60年的等待，终于苦思冥想出一条复仇大计——策反敌方炸碉堡。</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E9%81%97%E8%90%BD%E6%88%98%E5%A2%83/4967316/0/3bf33a87e950352a2e8e7ed85a43fbf2b3118b77?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss0.bdstatic.com/94o3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D142%2C0%2C360%2C513%3Bw%3D552%3Bq%3D70/sign=133fc5840a4f78f09444c0b344003e67/3bf33a87e950352a2e8e7ed85a43fbf2b3118b77.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
茱莉亚·哈勃
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
欧嘉·柯瑞兰寇
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
<a target=_blank href="/item/%E7%8E%8B%E6%99%93%E5%B7%8D">王晓巍</a>;詹佳
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
茱莉亚·哈勃是宇航员，也是杰克本体妻子。从天而降的太空舱里一个美丽的女人，茱莉亚闯入杰克生活后，杰克开始质疑自己所知的一切。
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
<li class="roleIntroduction-item ">
<a class="roleIntrodcution-picture" href="/pic/%E9%81%97%E8%90%BD%E6%88%98%E5%A2%83/4967316/0/3c6d55fbb2fb4316d28020aa29a4462308f7d347?fr=lemma" target = "_blank">
<img src="https://gss3.bdstatic.com/7Po3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/crop%3D63%2C0%2C395%2C562%3Bw%3D552%3Bq%3D70/sign=6516250d27738bd4d06ee8719cbdb4fa/3c6d55fbb2fb4316d28020aa29a4462308f7d347.jpg" alt=""/>
</a>
<dl class="roleIntrodcution-descritpion">
<dt>
<div class="role-name">
<span class="item-value">
维卡
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-actor">
<span class="item-key">演员</span><span class="item-value">
安德丽亚·瑞斯波罗格
</span>
</div>
<div class="role-voice">
<span class="item-key">配音</span>
<span class="item-value">
牟珈论;张琦
</span>
</div>
</dt>
<dd class="role-description">
<div>维卡是幸存者之一，与杰克共同留守地球，负责担任连系巡航的杰克与总部的通讯官。虽然杰克心中摇摆存疑，维卡总是要他别去质疑上司，全心全意接受眼前的一切。</div>
</dd>
</dl>
</li>
</ul>
<div class="expand-all-container">
